comments: Brown (MIL) makes marginal contact with Wright (DAL) on the perimeter.
Ilyasova (MIL) moves slightly laterally into Wright's (DAL) path during his drive however the contact is marginal.
Following the hand off, Brunson (DAL) clamps Hill's (MIL) arm and the contact affects his FOM.
Hill (MIL) briefly places a hand on the opposite side of Curry's (DAL) body during the inbound however the contact is marginal.
Ilyasova (MIL) makes incidental contact with Curry's (DAL) leg as Curry (DAL) slightly extends his leg following his jump shot attempt.
Korver (MIL) commits a take foul on Wright (DAL).
DiVincenzo (MIL) commits a take foul on Wright (DAL).
Wright (DAL) makes marginal contact with Hill's (MIL) body prior to cleanly dislodging the ball.
Finney-Smith's (DAL) arms are not in a legal position when the contact to Ilyasova's (MIL) arm occurs.
Ilyasova (MIL) makes marginal body contact to Brunson (DAL) prior to dislodging the ball.

call_type: Turnover: Lost Ball Out of Bounds
comments: After the ball is dislodged, Brunson (DAL) is the last player to touch the ball.
Curry (DAL) briefly grasps Hill's (MIL) jersey as they remain stationary and disengage from the screen.
Korver (MIL) commits a take foul on Jackson (DAL).
Hill (MIL) slightly extends his arm into Jackson's (DAL) body as he moves along his path during the drive. The marginal contact does not affect Jackson's ability to defend.
Hill (MIL) commits a take foul on Brunson (DAL).
Kleber (DAL) briefly places a hand on Antetokounmpo's (MIL) front in the back court, but Antetokoumpo is able to move through the marginal contact and continue along his original path.

Following the incidental foot to foot contact during the inbound, Matthews (MIL) falls to the floor and makes contact with Hardaway Jr.'s (DAL) leg that dislodges him and affects his ability to get to the pass. The contact occurs after the inbound pass is released but prior to the ball being touched inbounds. This is correctly assessed as a personal foul. The game clock is correctly reset to 00:11.9.
Kleber (DAL) makes marginal contact to Antetokounmpo's (MIL) arm that does not affect his driving shot attempt.
Antetokounmpo (MIL) commits a take foul on Hardaway Jr. (DAL).
Kleber (DAL) does not establish a legal guarding position in Antetokounmpo's (MIL) path when the body contact occurs during the driving shot attempt.
Porzingis (DAL) initiates some contact to Brown's (MIL) shoulder but the marginal contact does not affect his ability to get to the rebound.
Matthews (MIL) and Powell (DET) mutually engage and make incidental foot to foot contact during the rebound.
Porzingis (DAL) cleanly blocks Brown's (MIL) shot attempt near the rim.
Matthews (MIL) commits a take foul on Hardaway Jr. (DAL).
